<%- include('partials/header', {title: 'About - MERN Quiz'}) %>

<div class="about-container">
    <div class="about-header">
        <h1>About MERN Quiz</h1>
        <p class="about-subtitle">Your comprehensive platform for mastering the MERN stack</p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-content">
        <section class="about-section">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i> Our Mission</h2>
            <p>
                MERN Quiz is designed to help developers at all levels test and improve their knowledge of the MERN stack. 
                Whether you're a beginner learning the basics or an experienced developer looking to validate your skills, 
                our comprehensive quiz platform provides the perfect learning environment.
            </p>
            <p>
                We believe that hands-on practice and immediate feedback are essential for effective learning. 
                That's why our quiz provides detailed explanations for each question, helping you understand 
                not just what the correct answer is, but why it's correct.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="about-section">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-cogs"></i> How It Works</h2>
            <div class="features-list">
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-random"></i>
                    <div>
                        <h3>Randomized Questions</h3>
                        <p>Each quiz session presents 10 randomly selected questions from our database of 20+ carefully crafted questions, ensuring a unique experience every time.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
                    <div>
                        <h3>Detailed Analytics</h3>
                        <p>Get comprehensive feedback with category-wise performance analysis, time tracking, and detailed explanations for each question.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-infinity"></i>
                    <div>
                        <h3>Unlimited Attempts</h3>
                        <p>Take the quiz as many times as you want. Each attempt helps reinforce your learning and track your progress over time.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i>
                    <div>
                        <h3>Mobile Responsive</h3>
                        <p>Take the quiz on any device - desktop, tablet, or mobile. Our responsive design ensures a great experience everywhere.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="about-section">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-layer-group"></i> Technologies Covered</h2>
            <div class="tech-details">
                <div class="tech-detail">
                    <div class="tech-icon mongodb">
                        <i class="fas fa-leaf"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="tech-info">
                        <h3>MongoDB</h3>
                        <p>Learn about NoSQL databases, document structure, collections, queries, indexing, and MongoDB-specific concepts that are essential for modern web development.</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Document-based data model</li>
                            <li>Collections and databases</li>
                            <li>Query operations and aggregation</li>
                            <li>Indexing and performance</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="tech-detail">
                    <div class="tech-icon express">
                        <i class="fas fa-server"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="tech-info">
                        <h3>Express.js</h3>
                        <p>Master web framework concepts including routing, middleware, HTTP methods, request-response cycles, and building RESTful APIs.</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Routing and middleware</li>
                            <li>HTTP methods and status codes</li>
                            <li>Request and response handling</li>
                            <li>Error handling and debugging</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="tech-detail">
                    <div class="tech-icon react">
                        <i class="fab fa-react"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="tech-info">
                        <h3>React</h3>
                        <p>Understand JSX, component lifecycle, hooks, state management, props, and modern React development patterns and best practices.</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>JSX syntax and components</li>
                            <li>Hooks (useState, useEffect, etc.)</li>
                            <li>Component lifecycle methods</li>
                            <li>State management and props</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="tech-detail">
                    <div class="tech-icon nodejs">
                        <i class="fab fa-node-js"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="tech-info">
                        <h3>Node.js</h3>
                        <p>Explore runtime environment concepts, npm package management, modules, asynchronous programming, and server-side JavaScript development.</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Runtime environment basics</li>
                            <li>NPM package management</li>
                            <li>Module system (CommonJS, ES6)</li>
                            <li>Asynchronous programming patterns</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="about-section">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-code"></i> Built With</h2>
            <p>This quiz application is built using modern web technologies and follows best practices for performance, accessibility, and user experience.</p>
            <div class="built-with">
                <div class="tech-stack">
                    <div class="stack-item">
                        <i class="fab fa-node-js"></i>
                        <span>Node.js</span>
                        <small>Runtime Environment</small>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stack-item">
                        <i class="fas fa-server"></i>
                        <span>Express.js</span>
                        <small>Web Framework</small>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stack-item">
                        <i class="fas fa-file-code"></i>
                        <span>EJS</span>
                        <small>Template Engine</small>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stack-item">
                        <i class="fas fa-database"></i>
                        <span>Sessions</span>
                        <small>State Management</small>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="about-section">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-chart-bar"></i> Quiz Statistics</h2>
            <div class="stats-grid">
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-question-circle"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-info">
                        <h3>20+</h3>
                        <p>Total Questions</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-layer-group"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-info">
                        <h3>4</h3>
                        <p>Categories</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-clock"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-info">
                        <h3>~5 min</h3>
                        <p>Average Time</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-graduation-cap"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-info">
                        <h3>70%</h3>
                        <p>Passing Score</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>

    <div class="cta-section">
        <h2>Ready to Test Your Knowledge?</h2>
        <p>Start your MERN stack assessment journey today and see how much you know!</p>
        <a href="/quiz" class="cta-button">
            <i class="fas fa-play"></i>
            Start Quiz Now
        </a>
    </div>
</div>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
